STYLES.md
# Upstream apriltag-imgs mosaics are build-time inputs to
# scripts/chunk-mosaics.ts. The runtime ships the chunked PNGs under
# public/resources/apriltag/ instead; the unchunked mosaics are
# regenerable via scripts/fetch-mosaics.ts and never checked in.
public/resources/*_mosaic.png
